          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Butcher Block Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Agriculture to make (or guarantee) loans and award grants for establishing, expanding, and otherwise supporting livestock and meat processing and related activities.</p>]]>
        </text>
