      <summary>
        <versionCode>07</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2022-06-14</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Reported to House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2022-10-04T11:26:40Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Butcher Block Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Agriculture (USDA) to make (or guarantee) loans and award grants for establishing, expanding, and otherwise supporting livestock and poultry processing and related activities.</p> <p>In awarding grants and making or guaranteeing loans, USDA shall prioritize applicants that have experience in livestock and poultry processing and can quickly scale-up to increase overall processing capacity in the region involved.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
